#: projects/index.php:12
msgid ""
"The Xfce project contains several separated projects for each part of the "
"desktop. Some projects have their own project pages to provide additional "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Xfce-projektet indeholder flere separate projekter til hver del af "
"skrivebordet. Nogle projekter har deres egne projektpakker til at give "
"yderligere information."

#: projects/index.php:15
msgid "Core Components"
msgstr "Kernekomponenter"

#: projects/index.php:22
msgid ""
"It manages the placement of application windows on the screen, provides "
"window decorations and manages workspaces or virtual desktops."
msgstr ""
"Det håndterer placeringen af programvinduer på skærmen, sørger for "
"vinduesdekorationer og styrer arbejdsområder eller virtuelle skriveborde."

#: projects/index.php:29
msgid ""
"The panel is a bar which allows you to have at all times program launchers, "
"panel menus, a clock, a desktop switcher and more."
msgstr ""
"Panelet er en linje som gør dig i stand til at have programstartere, menuer,"
" et ur, en skrivebordsskifter og mere."

#: projects/index.php:37
msgid ""
"This program sets the background image and provides a root window menu, "
"desktop icons or minimized icons and a windows list."
msgstr ""
"Dette program sætte baggrundsbilledet og leverer en root-vinduesmenu, "
"skrivebordsikoner og minimerede ikoner og en vinduesliste."

#: projects/index.php:44
msgid ""
"The session manager controls all aspects of the startup and the shutdown of "
"the user session."
msgstr ""
"Sessionshåndteringen styrer alle aspekter af opstarten og nedlukningen af "
"brugersessionen."

#: projects/index.php:52
msgid "It allows you to configure every detail of your desktop environment."
msgstr ""
"Giver dig mulighed for at konfigurere alle detaljerne af dit "
"skrivebordsmiljø."

#: projects/index.php:60
msgid ""
"Thunar is a modern file manager designed from the ground up to be fast and "
"easy-to-use."
msgstr ""
"Thunar er et moderne program til håndtering af filer, designet fra bunden "
"til at være hurtig og let at bruge."

#: projects/index.php:68
msgid ""
"Allows you to search, launch and find information about applications "
"installed on your system."
msgstr ""
"Giver dig mulighed for at søge, starte og finde information om programmer "
"som er installeret på dit system."

#: projects/index.php:76
msgid "Manages the power sources of the computer and connected devices."
msgstr "Håndterer strømkilderne for computeren og tilsluttede enheder."

#: projects/index.php:82
msgid "Xfce Libraries"
msgstr "Xfce-biblioteker"

#: projects/index.php:84
msgid "Widgets library for the Xfce desktop environment."
msgstr "Widgetsbibliotek til Xfce-skrivebordsmiljøet."

#: projects/index.php:92
msgid "Simple client-server configuration storage and query system."
msgstr ""
"Simpelt klient-server-baseret konfigurationslagrings- og anmodningssystem."

#: projects/index.php:99
msgid "Applications"
msgstr "Programmer"

#: projects/index.php:106
msgid ""
"Terminal is a modern terminal emulator featuring tabs and transparent "
"backgrounds."
msgstr ""
"Terminal er en moderne terminalemulator med faneblade og gennemsigtige "
"baggrunde."

#: projects/index.php:112
msgid "Xfburn"
msgstr "Xfburn"

#: projects/index.php:114
msgid "Xfburn is an application to create and burn CD's and DVD's."
msgstr "Xfburn er et program til at skabe og brænde cd'er og dvd'er."

#: projects/index.php:119
msgid "Image Viewer"
msgstr "Billedfremviser"

#: projects/index.php:121
msgid "Ristretto is a lightweight image viewer."
msgstr "Ristretto er en letvægtsbilledfremviser."

#: projects/index.php:127
msgid "Screen Saver"
msgstr "Pauseskærm"

#: projects/index.php:129
msgid "A simple screen saver and locker."
msgstr "En simpel pauseskærm og skærmlåser."

#: projects/index.php:135
msgid "Screen Shooter"
msgstr "Skærmbillede"

#: projects/index.php:137
msgid "An application to take screenshots."
msgstr "Et program til at tage skærmbilleder."

#: projects/index.php:145
msgid "A simple text editor."
msgstr "En simpel tekstredigering."

#: projects/index.php:151
msgid "Notifications"
msgstr "Underretninger"

#: projects/index.php:153
msgid "Easily themable notification daemon with transparency effects."
msgstr ""
"Underretningsdæmon som let kan bruge temaer med gennemsigtige effekter."

#: 404.php:1
msgid "Page not found"
msgstr "Siden blev ikke fundet"

#: 404.php:5
msgid ""
"We're sorry, the page or file you requested was not found on this server."
msgstr ""
"Beklager. Den anmodede side eller fil blev ikke fundet på denne server."

#: 404.php:7
msgid ""
"If you clicked on a link that brought you to this page, or you have reached "
"this page through a search engine or bookmark, it could very well be that "
"the page you were looking for was removed, renamed or temporary unavailable."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du klikkede på et link som bragte dig til denne side eller du har nået "
"denne siden gennem en søgemaskine eller et bogmærke, så kan det meget vel "
"være at siden du ledte efter er fjernet, omdøbt eller midlertidigt "
"utilgængelig."

#: 404.php:10
msgid ""
"Please try one of the following methods to find the page you are looking "
"for:"
msgstr ""
"Prøv venligst en af de følgende metoder for at finde siden du leder efter:"

#: 404.php:14
msgid ""
"If you typed the page address in the Address bar, make sure that it is "
"spelled correctly."
msgstr ""
"Sørg for at sidens adresse i adresselinjen er stavet korrekt, hvis du selv "
"har indtastet den."

#: 404.php:16
msgid "Click the Back button to try another link."
msgstr "Klik på Tilbage-knappen for at prøve et andet link."

